                        <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18490820-1608-offence-1 t18490820-geo-4"></join>St. Leonard's, Shoreditch</placeName>, and stealing 8 yards of printed cotton, and other goods, value 9<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. 6<hi rend="italic">d</hi>.; his goods: having been before convicted.</rs>
